OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783687767
OL,3,CSouthport families want
OL,4,C'accountability' from second phase of
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe first phase found the murders of
OL,8,FBebe King, Elsie Dot Stancombe and
OL,9,FAlice da Silva Aguiar could have been
OL,10,Fprevented if the killer's parents and
OL,11,Fauthorities had intervened in the
OL,12,Fyears leading up to the attack.
OL,14,FPhase Two, which is being held at the
OL,15,FInternational Dispute Resolution
OL,16,FCentre in London, began with a
OL,17,Fminute's silence on Wednesday 8 July,
OL,18,Ffor the victims of the attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783687767
OL,3,CSouthport families want
OL,4,C'accountability' from second phase of
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FChris Walker, solicitor for the
OL,8,Ffamilies of the three girls killed in
OL,9,Fthe Southport attack, says there must
OL,10,Fbe accountability, ahead of the start
OL,11,Fof Phase Two of the Southport Inquiry
OL,13,FChris Walker, solicitor for the
OL,14,Ffamilies of the three murdered
OL,15,Fschoolgirls, said: "The families are
OL,16,Fstill living through this horror movie.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783687767
OL,3,CSouthport families want
OL,4,C'accountability' from second phase of
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"Listening to the failings and issues
OL,8,Fis very difficult for them. The
OL,9,Ffamilies' main priority is to ensure
OL,10,Fatrocities like this never happen
OL,11,Fagain.
OL,13,F"We have to have systems in place
OL,14,Fwhere people are held accountable."
OL,16,FWhat will be the most significant
OL,17,Felements of Phase Two?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783687767
OL,3,CSouthport families want
OL,4,C'accountability' from second phase of
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe second part of the Inquiry will
OL,8,Fexamine how to deal with individuals
OL,9,Fwho pose a risk of extreme violence,
OL,10,Fbut where ideology is not the primary
OL,11,Fdriver, as well as the role of the
OL,12,Finternet and social media in
OL,13,Finfluencing and enabling them.
OL,15,FIn an opening statement at the
OL,16,FInquiry, chairman Sir Adrian Fulford
OL,17,Fsaid he was "resolutely optimistic"
OL,18,Fthat past failures and means of
OL,19,Fimplementing real change could be
OL,20,Fidentified.
OL,26,@yD@MOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36806
