CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783687767
OL,3,CSouthport families want
OL,4,C'accountability' from second phase of
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FHe said: "More than anything else,
OL,8,Fyoung people must be diverted from the
OL,9,Fthoughts and impulses which motivated
OL,10,FAR in July 2024.
OL,12,F"We are confronted with a growing
OL,13,Fchallenge from violence-fixated
OL,14,Findividuals, who all too often are not
OL,15,Facting out of an adherence to a
OL,16,Fparticular ideology.
OL,18,F"Instead, the reasons for their
OL,19,Finterest in violence are various and,
OL,20,Fas a consequence, they can be
OL,21,Fextremely difficult to identify.
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783687767
OL,3,CSouthport families want
OL,4,C'accountability' from second phase of
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"All too often, they will be acting
OL,8,Fentirely alone, having spent endless
OL,9,Fhours in solitude, relentlessly,
OL,10,Fonline."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
