OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783687767
OL,3,CSouthport families want
OL,4,C'accountability' from second phase of
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FSir Adrian added: "The victims and
OL,8,Ftheir families will be at the very
OL,9,Fcentre of our work during phase two,
OL,10,Fnot least because they have the right
OL,11,Fto expect that we remain ` as I hope
OL,12,Fwill be the case ` unwaveringly
OL,13,Ffocussed, efficient and effective in
OL,14,Four work and that we identify,
OL,15,Fwherever they exist, the changes of
OL,16,Fsubstance that must be made as to how
OL,17,Fwe address those who have a dangerous
OL,18,Fpreoccupation with significant
OL,19,Fviolence."
OL,26,@oD@SOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
