OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783687767
OL,3,CSouthport families want
OL,4,C'accountability' from second phase of
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FWhat was the outcome of Phase One of
OL,8,Fthe Southport Inquiry?
OL,10,FThe first phase was published in April
OL,11,F2026. The report found that the attack
OL,12,Fin July 2024 'could and should' have
OL,13,Fbeen stopped if the killer's parents
OL,14,Fand state agencies had acted sooner.
OL,16,FIts chair, Sir Adrian Fulford, has
OL,17,Fmade 67 recommendations in a 700-page
OL,18,Freport into the attack by 17-year-old
OL,19,FAxel Rudakubana in July 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1783687767
OL,3,CSouthport families want
OL,4,C'accountability' from second phase of
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe report followed a nine-week public
OL,8,Finquiry at Liverpool Town Hall in
OL,9,F2025. It focused criticism on a number
OL,10,Fof state agencies along with the
OL,11,Fparents of the killer - referred to as
OL,12,F'AR' throughout the inquiry.
OL,14,FRudakubana, now 19, was given a life
OL,15,Fsentence, with a minimum term of 52
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,FThe government announced on Thursday 2
OL,19,FJuly that it accepts all of the
OL,20,Frecommendations "in full".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
